==Description==

The '''Beastball''' is a type of [[Pokéballs|Pokéball]]. It automatically tries to catch a wild Ultra Beast after defeating it if a Beastball is Set to any of the catching options.

==Details==

A specialized Pokéball to capture Pokémon with, it can catch Ultra Beasts. Beastballs can't capture wild pokémons other than the Ultra Beasts.

